    • onAddCustomerSaveBtnClicked

      void onAddCustomerSaveBtnClicked(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
      Action even for when the save button is clicked. Grabs values from the text fields and makes a new customer class based off them. If there are missing values, throw an error. If there are no errors, insert the added customer into the database using the Customer Query insert method.
